THAT SHE WAS

13:28.330 --> 13:30.150
AND ALWAYS WILL BE.

13:30.160 --> 13:31.889
YOU KNOW
WHO SHE WAS ?

13:31.900 --> 13:33.219
ABSOLUTELY.

13:33.230 --> 13:35.596
AND I'M A BIG
FAN OF HERS.

13:39.760 --> 13:41.091
HEY, RICO.

13:41.100 --> 13:43.898
HOLY MOLY.

13:43.900 --> 13:46.391
FEEL THEM,
THEY'RE REALLY HARD.

13:46.400 --> 13:47.856
NO THANKS.

13:47.860 --> 13:49.225
LIKE A ROCK.

13:49.230 --> 13:51.926
SEE HOW THEY'RE
ALL COCKEYED ?

13:51.930 --> 13:54.592
THEY GOT THIS LOW-CUT
FLIMSY THING THEY WANT HER IN

13:54.600 --> 13:56.750
AND THEY SAID
ABSOLUTELY NO BRA.

13:56.760 --> 13:59.354
SHIT, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE HECK I'M GONNA DO.

13:59.360 --> 14:02.693
MAYBE I COULD LIKE,
TAPE 'EM TOGETHER SOMEHOW.

14:02.700 --> 14:04.395
YOU KNOW WHERE
THIS STUFF GOES ?

14:04.400 --> 14:06.425
I PUT IT IN THE WRONG PLACE
DAVID'LL BITCH AT ME FOR A WEEK.

14:06.430 --> 14:08.648
TOP LEFT, ABOVE
THE PURPLE STUFF.

14:08.660 --> 14:10.093
WELL, BOYS,

14:10.100 --> 14:13.251
THIS JUST MIGHT BE OUR
HIGHEST-PROFIT-MARGIN
FUNERAL THIS YEAR.

14:13.260 --> 14:14.420
SHE'S RICH, HUH ?

14:14.430 --> 14:15.897
THE GUY WHO'S
PAYING FOR IT IS.

14:15.900 --> 14:17.856
SHE LOOKS SO
FAMILIAR TO ME.

14:17.860 --> 14:18.827
SHE'S AN ACTRESS.

14:18.830 --> 14:20.195
VIVECA ST. JOHN.

14:20.200 --> 14:22.760
OH, MY GOD,
YOU'RE RIGHT.

14:22.760 --> 14:24.455
THAT'S HER ?

14:24.460 --> 14:26.098
APPARENTLY SHE WAS
QUITE TALENTED.

14:26.100 --> 14:27.692
SHE WAS
A PORNO STAR.

14:27.700 --> 14:29.452
WHAT ?

14:29.460 --> 14:31.690
DAVID, SHE WAS HUGE, LIKE
BACK IN THE MID-TO-LATE 80$.

14:31.700 --> 14:33.452
OH, COME ON, YOU NEVER
SAW ANY OF HER VIDEOS ?

14:33.460 --> 14:34.893
