WOULD YOU ASK COLONEL SANDERS
FOR HIS SECRET RECIPE ?

47:06.400 --> 47:08.493
OH, C'MON,
I'M NOT GONNA TELL.

47:13.030 --> 47:16.352
I STUCK A CAN OF CAT FOOD
UNDER EACH ONE.

47:16.360 --> 47:19.397
MY SISTER-IN-LAW DID
A CAT FOOD COMMERCIAL.

47:19.400 --> 47:22.494
WE'VE GOT
LIKE 10 CASES.

47:25.060 --> 47:26.425
HEY.

47:27.360 --> 47:28.759
I'M LARRY WADD.

47:28.760 --> 47:30.648
( applause )

47:31.500 --> 47:33.229
YOU KNOW...

47:33.230 --> 47:36.893
I MET VIVECA ST. JOHN BEFORE
SHE EVEN DID HER FIRST VIDEO.

47:38.800 --> 47:39.653
YEAH.

47:39.660 --> 47:41.150
SHE WAS...

47:41.160 --> 47:45.358
SHE WAS THE FLUFFER ON THE SET
OF "DIRTY LARRY THREE".

47:47.260 --> 47:48.454
SHE WAS...

47:48.460 --> 47:52.692
FRIENDLY,
SHE WAS EAGER.

47:53.800 --> 47:55.722
I CAN HONESTLY SAY

47:55.730 --> 47:58.290
I'VE NEVER RECEIVED
A BETTER BLOW JOB IN MY LIFE.

47:58.300 --> 48:00.052
AND NOBODY WAS
EVEN FILMING IT.

48:00.060 --> 48:02.597
( applause )

48:04.560 --> 48:08.758
( female )
WHEN I FIRST MET VIVECA,
I MET HER ON "DEEP DIVING".

48:08.760 --> 48:10.796
THANK YOU.

48:11.700 --> 48:14.157
AND I HAD NEVER GONE DOWN
ON A GIRL BEFORE,

48:14.160 --> 48:15.957
SO, NATURALLY
I WAS NERVOUS,

48:15.960 --> 48:19.726
BUT VIVECA WAS SO WARM
AND RELAXED ABOUT IT.

48:19.730 --> 48:22.290
SHE REALLY
PUT ME AT EASE.

48:22.300 --> 48:26.054
HER AND THE TWO XANAX
SHE GAVE ME.

48:26.060 --> 48:30.292
WHEN I FIRST HAD TO DO
A DOUBLE PENETRATION,

48:30.300 --> 48:32.655
I WAS LIKE
A TOTAL WRECK.

48:32.660 --> 48:35.754
BUT VIVECA CAME THROUGH

48:35.760 --> 48:38.695
LIKE SUCH
THE PRO SHE IS.

48:39.800 --> 48:41.859
I MEAN WAS.

48:48.830 --> 48:51.390
NATE, WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON IN THERE ?

48:51.400 --> 48:52.992
A FUNERAL.

48:53.000 --> 48:54.490
FOR WHOM ?

48:54.500 --> 48:55.922
A PROSTITUTE ?

48:57.900 --> 49:02.451
A WOMAN WHO WAS A STAR
OF ADULT VIDEOS.

49:02.460 --> 49:05.327
MOM, WE'RE GONNA CLEAR
LIKE EIGHT GRAND FROM THIS.

49:05.330 --> 49:07.798
WE CAN FINALLY PAY FOR
ALL THAT AIR CONDITIONING WORK.

49:12.960 --> 49:15.622
I'M JUST GLAD YOUR SISTER
IS AT SCHOOL.

49:16.460 --> 49:17.791
IT WAS AWFUL.

49:17.800 --> 49:19.552
THEY WERE LIKE
BEST FRIENDS.

49:19.560 --> 49:22.028
THEY WERE BOTH
LIKE CHEERLEADERS

49:22.030 --> 49:24.055
FOR THIS TOTALLY
PLASTIC WAY OF LIFE.

49:24.060 --> 49:26.358
LIKE, SPINNING CLASS
SOLVES EVERYTHING.

49:26.360 --> 49:28.749
AND THEY'RE BOTH
HOT FOR THE SAME GUY,

49:28.760 --> 49:30.625
IT WAS CREEPY.

49:39.400 --> 49:40.890
MY MOM'S--

49:42.500 --> 49:44.559
MY MOM IS JUST
SO FUCKING SAD.

49:44.560 --> 49:48.291
I WISH I COULD
HELP HER.

49:51.660 --> 49:53.594
SO, HELP HER.

49:55.130 --> 49:58.019
NOW, MRS. MURDOCH,
SOME PEOPLE PREFER

49:58.030 --> 49:59.520
THE SOLEMNITY
OF A CHURCH

49:59.530 --> 50:02.158
AND ST. BARTHOLOMEW IS
A BEAUTIFUL SETTING.

50:02.160 --> 50:06.449
HERE, HOWEVER, ONE IS MORE FREE
TO CUSTOMIZE THE SERVICE.

50:06.460 --> 50:08.291
I'M SORRY
TO INTERRU PT.

50:08.300 --> 50:10.256
I JUST HAD TO
TELL SOMEBODY.

50:10.260 --> 50:13.297
VIVECA LOOKS
SO GREAT.

50:13.300 --> 50:16.997
HER TITS HAVE NEVER
LOOKED BETTER.

50:18.900 --> 50:21.721
SHE WAS LIKE
A SISTER TO ME.

50:29.960 --> 50:32.497
I'M SO GLAD THAT
YOU'RE PLEASED.

50:32.500 --> 50:36.049
WE WANT TO REMEMBER HER
AT HER VERY BEST, DON'T WE ?

50:36.060 --> 50:40.724
I'M SORRY, BUT I'M HELPING
SOME OTHER PEOPLE RIGHT NOW.

50:40.730 --> 50:42.527
OKAY.

50:42.530 --> 50:43.952
I'LL TALK TO YOU
AFTER THE SERVICE ?

50:43.960 --> 50:45.723
OKAY.

50:52.100 --> 50:54.591
I THINK WE'LL HAVE DAD'S
SERVICE AT THE CHURCH.

50:54.600 --> 50:56.329
FINE.

50:56.330 --> 50:58.218
I'M NOT
A RELIGIOUS MAN.

50:58.230 --> 51:00.448
BUT I DO
BELIEVE IN GOD.

51:00.460 --> 51:03.623
IF I WERE TO MAKE
A LIST OF THE THINGS

51:03.630 --> 51:07.020
I THANK GOD
FOR THE MOST...

51:09.200 --> 51:12.192
FUCKING VIV WOULD BE
AT THE TOP OF THAT LIST.

51:12.200 --> 51:15.954
SHE WAS A GODDAMN
FORCE OF NATURE.

51:15.960 --> 51:20.750
AND I LOVED HER AND I KNOW
GOD LOVED HER TOO.

51:20.760 --> 51:23.524
I KNOW HE KNEW JUST
WHAT HE WAS DOING.

51:23.530 --> 51:27.091
AND HOW MUCH JOY...

51:27.100 --> 51:30.524
SHE WOULD BRING
TO THE WORLD.

51:42.000 --> 51:45.595
FOR DAVID JAMES FISHER,
CHOSEN DEACON IN YOUR CHURCH,

51:45.600 --> 51:47.522
WE PRAY TO YOU,
OH LORD.

51:47.530 --> 51:49.555
( congregation )
LORD, HEAR OUR PRAYER.

51:49.560 --> 51:51.596
THAT HE MAY FAITHFULLY
FULFILL THE DUTIES

51:51.600 --> 51:52.999
OF THIS MINISTRY,

51:53.000 --> 51:56.049
BUILD UP YOUR CHURCH
AND GLORIFY YOUR NAME,

51:56.060 --> 51:57.994
WE PRAY TO YOU,
OH LORD.

51:58.000 --> 52:00.093
LORD, HEAR OUR PRAYER.

52:00.100 --> 52:02.295
THAT BY THE INDWELLING
OF THE HOLY SPIRIT

52:02.300 --> 52:04.393
HE MAY BE SUSTAINED
AND ENCOURAGED

52:04.400 --> 52:06.095
TO PERSEVERE
TO THE END,

52:06.100 --> 52:07.897
WE PRAY TO YOU,
OH LORD.

52:07.900 --> 52:09.697
LORD, HEAR OUR PRAYER.

52:09.700 --> 52:12.999
FOR ALL WHO FEAR GOD AND
BELIEVE IN YOU, LORD CHRIST,

52:13.000 --> 52:17.221
THAT OUR DIVISIONS MAY CEASE
AND THAT ALL MAY BE AS ONE

52:17.230 --> 52:19.551
AS YOU AND
THE FATHER ARE ONE.

52:19.560 --> 52:22.097
WE PRAY TO YOU,
OH LORD.

52:22.100 --> 52:24.557
LORD, HEAR OUR PRAYER.

52:38.200 --> 52:40.395
WAY TO GO, DAVE.

52:41.500 --> 52:43.923
NOW ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS JOIN THE KIWANIS CLUB

52:43.930 --> 52:46.148
AND FISHER & SONS WILL
HAVE ALL OUR BASES COVERED.

52:48.000 --> 52:49.399
WHERE'S KEITH ?

52:49.400 --> 52:51.789
HE'S JUST
A FRIEND, NATE.

52:55.430 --> 52:57.990
VERY GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

52:58.460 --> 52:59.859
HELLO.

53:03.330 --> 53:05.821
SO MOM, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING TOMORROW NIGHT ?

53:05.830 --> 53:08.094
NOTHING AS FAR
AS I KNOW.

53:08.100 --> 53:09.556
WHY ?

53:09.560 --> 53:12.120
I THOUGHT MAYBE YOU'D
WANT TO GO SEE A MOVIE

53:12.130 --> 53:14.257
OR RENT A MOVIE
OR SOMETHING.

53:14.260 --> 53:17.991
OKAY, BUT IF YOU CRY,
THE WHOLE THING IS OFF.

53:20.700 --> 53:22.918
THANKS FOR
COMING TODAY.

53:22.930 --> 53:24.921
I KNOW YOU MUST'VE
FOUND THIS ALL A LITTLE--

53:24.930 --> 53:26.625
ARE YOU KIDDING ?
I LOVED IT.

53:26.630 --> 53:28.894
ALL THAT PAGEANTRY,
IT'S SO TRIPPY,

53:28.900 --> 53:30.652
IT'S LIKE
A FELLINI MOVIE.

53:30.660 --> 53:32.651
WELL, IT WAS KIND OF COOL
BEING WITH YOU HERE.

53:32.660 --> 53:34.389
IN FRONT OF GOD
AND EVERYBODY.

53:37.530 --> 53:40.693
YOU DON'T REALLY
BELIEVE IN GOD, DO YOU ?

53:40.700 --> 53:42.349
WELL, YEAH.

53:42.360 --> 53:45.488
I MEAN, I DON'T BELIEVE
IN SOME BEARDED OLD WHITE MAN

53:45.500 --> 53:47.149
UP IN A CLOUD, BUT...

53:47.160 --> 53:49.048
I BELIEVE
IN SOMETHING.

53:49.060 --> 53:52.291
SOME SORT OF UNDEFINABLE
CREATIVE FORCE.

53:52.300 --> 53:55.224
I THINK IT'S JUST
ALL TOTALLY RAN DOM.

53:55.230 --> 53:56.652
REALLY ?

53:56.660 --> 53:58.525
YEAH.

53:58.530 --> 54:00.498
WE LIVE, WE DIE.

54:00.500 --> 54:02.889
ULTIMATELY, NOTHING
MEANS ANYTHING.

54:02.900 --> 54:05.619
HOW CAN YOU
LIVE LIKE THAT ?

54:05.630 --> 54:06.858
I DON'T KNOW.

54:06.860 --> 54:08.555
SOMETIMES I WAKE UP
SO FUCKING EMPTY,

54:08.560 --> 54:10.528
I WISH I'D NEVER
BEEN BORN,

54:10.530 --> 54:13.124
BUT WHAT CHOICE
DO I HAVE ?

